-- Azerbaijan Approves 308 Million-Euro Loan Agreement With Serbia
-- B y   Z u l f u g a r   A g a y e v
-- 2012-04-06T11:59:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/azerbaijan-approves-308-million-euro-loan-agreement-with-serbia.html
Azerbaijan ’s lawmakers approved an
agreement today to give a 308 million-euro ($403 million) loan
to  Serbia  to fund  road construction  in the Balkan country.  The 25-year loan will pay interest at an annual rate of 4
percent, Akif Tavakkuloglu, head of the parliament’s press
service in the capital, Baku, said by phone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zulfugar Agayev in Baku at 
